The paper discusses the use of a bi-directional array view mechanism for scientific file formats, which aims to make declarative array manipulations interoperable with imperative file-centric analyses. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the database (cs.DB), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), scientific computing (cs.SC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and software engineering (cs.SE) sub-categories.
